name: Boxframey
description:
Speed up your wireframing process with Boxframey, pre-made wireframe sections.


What's in the file:

10+ sections

30+ section variations

Local color styles

Customizeable - create your own section

Regularly update

Bonus! Landing Page UI mockup.
